title: Yulia Kornievets
text:
Yulia Kornievets is a Ukrainian <a href="women%27s%20association%20football">footballer</a> who plays as a <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29%23Striker">striker</a>. She previously played in Russia for <a href="FC%20Zorky%20Krasnogorsk%20%28women%29">Zorky Krasnogorsk</a> and <a href="FC%20Mordovochka%20Saransk">Mordovochka Saransk</a>, and in <a href="Ukrainian%20Women%27s%20League">Ukraine</a> for <a href="Lehenda%20Chernihiv">Lehenda Chernihiv</a>, with which she has also played the <a href="UEFA%20Women%27s%20Cup">European Cup</a>. She is a member of the <a href="Ukraine%20women%27s%20national%20football%20team">Ukrainian national team</a>.
Club career.
Kornievets played in the Spanish <a href="Primera%20Divisi%C3%B3n%20%28women%29">Primera División</a> for <a href="Sporting%20de%20Huelva">Sporting de Huelva</a> between 2018 and 2019.
